QueryCallback.name: GetJuvenileWarrantsListEventQuery
QueryCallback.whereClause: WARRANTTYPECD LIKE ? AND JUVFIRSTNAME LIKE ? AND JUVLASTNAME LIKE ? AND coalesce(WARRANTSTATUSCD,'') like ? AND WACTIVATIONSTAT like ? AND WACKNOWLEDGESTAT like ? AND coalesce(JUVNUMBER, '') like ? AND WSIGNEDSTATUSCD like ? AND coalesce(REFERRALNUMBER, '') like ?

QueryCallback.name: GetJuvenileWarrantsForAcknowledgeEventQuery
QueryCallback.whereClause: JUVFIRSTNAME LIKE ? AND JUVLASTNAME LIKE ? AND WACTIVATIONSTAT ='NA' AND WARRANTSTATUSCD = 'P' AND WACKNOWLEDGESTAT = 'NP' AND WARRANTTYPECD = ?

QueryCallback.name: GetJuvenileWarrantsForServiceSignatureUpdateEventQuery
QueryCallback.whereClause: JUVFIRSTNAME LIKE ? AND JUVLASTNAME LIKE ? AND WARRANTSTATUSCD LIKE ? AND SERVERTRNSGNSTAT LIKE ? AND WARRANTTYPECD IN ('ARR', 'OIC', 'DTA')

QueryCallback.name: GetJuvenileWarrantsForManageServiceEventQuery
QueryCallback.whereClause: JUVFIRSTNAME LIKE ? AND JUVLASTNAME LIKE ? AND WARRANTSTATUSCD LIKE ? AND WACTIVATIONSTAT LIKE ?

QueryCallback.name: GetJuvenileWarrantsForManageReleaseDecisionEventQuery

QueryCallback.name: GetJuvenileWarrantsForViewEventQuery
QueryCallback.whereClause: JUVFIRSTNAME LIKE ? AND JUVLASTNAME LIKE ? AND VARCHAR(COALESCE(OFFICERDEPTCD,'')) LIKE ? AND VARCHAR(COALESCE(WORIGUSER_ID,'')) LIKE ? AND VARCHAR(COALESCE(WARRANTTYPECD,'')) LIKE ?

QueryCallback.name: GetJuvenileWarrantsForReleaseEvent
QueryCallback.whereClause: JUVFIRSTNAME LIKE ? AND JUVLASTNAME LIKE ? AND WARRANTSTATUSCD = 'E' AND RELEASEDECISION IS NULL

QueryCallback.name: GetJuvenileWarrantServicesEventQuery

QueryCallback.name: GetJuvenileWarrantServiceInfoEventQuery
